data.description: Welcome to this incredible 4-bed, 3-bath home now available for sale. This 2 story home is a true entertainer's paradise, offering three separate living spaces, there is plenty of room for relaxation, entertainment, and quality family time. Prewired with surround sound down stairs and up stairs. One of the highlights of this property is the solar panel(PAID OFF Solar Panels) heated pool with Hot Tub, perfect for year-round enjoyment. The window shutters throughout the home not only add a touch of elegance but also provide privacy and control over natural light. Enjoy nearby amenities such as parks, shopping centers, and schools. This is an exceptional opportunity to own a home that seamlessly blends comfort, style, and entertainment. MOVE IN READY!  DONT MISS OUT!
